claim.claim-text:
1. An inkjet ink comprising:
a pigment;
a water-soluble resin having a hydrophobic group, the water-soluble resin including a part adsorbed to the pigment and a part not adsorbed to the pigment;
an inclusion compound comprising cyclodextrin or a cyclodextrin derivative; and
water,
wherein the part not adsorbed of the water-soluble resin has a mass ratio to the inclusion compound in a range of 1.60 to 9.00.
